{"tid":1421020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚過後，我從一個前線救火隊暫時退低做冷氣軍師。對不起，前線兄弟。","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:29:35.000Z","uid":263230,"like":70,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f3bbd94e3044b718abb638ae8dbd669c3233217d","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"//仇恨會腐蝕一個人的智慧和良知，敵人意識將毒化一個民族的精神，煽動起你死我活的殘酷鬥爭，毀掉一個社會的寬容和人性，阻礙一個國家走向自由民主的進程。//<br />\n<br />\n劉曉波的最後陳述<br />\n<br />\n正文：<br />\n<br />\n作為一個27歲的人，相比好多前線手足可能比較老，但又未去到30歲中年階段。經過尋日我真係攰，暫時休息一下。分享一下小小感受，想比前線手足知道，呢個亦係前線勇武抗爭永遠要面對的困境同難題，希望前線認真諗下點解決。<br />\n<br />\n尋日一直發夢係近屋企的荃灣，當係新界南狗總出左蛋之後同大隊散左，最後番左荃公見到大隊討論去向，有人話去荔枝角，我就選擇想去北角睇下福建幫。係地鐵見到荃灣傳出有藍衫即刻番轉頭，大隊話mtr集合，沿途撞到手足係荃新天橋，之後見到大家係大河道紅綠燈眾緊，行左去南豐停左。最後番大河道決定話一隊人行到荃西，有藍衫就拜訪無就散水，一隊人原點留守到十半。最後我去左荃西散，結果又係有黑社會砍人。<br />\n<br />\n以下係想講的重點，<br />\n<br />\n1. 點解次次大隊聚埋一齊永遠搵唔到黑社會，人一少黑社會又出黎搞事？諗落其實好簡單，大隊有好多人，加上附近街坊。黑社會/狗要搵人入黎收風其實好易，所有現場消息對方要知的話一定可以一手知得到，正如哨兵一樣。相反，要計劃行動我地要factcheck, 所有風向好難3幾分鐘就核實到，亦係我地唔會主動搵到黑社會的原因。<br />\n<br />\n點樣係前線現場，做到最保障到手足安全的決策同共識，相信要大家想認真深思。令手足受傷不特止，最後仲要內鬥屌其他手足，最後只會令不同的手足灰心失望。<br />\n<br />\n2. 差唔多時間，北角又有白衫人。好想大家睇番呢個post, 我係北角福建人 連登仔同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxbtBT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxbtBT</a><br />\n<br />\n藍衫人同河妖握手，而河妖係荃灣有辦事處，可以想像到其實點解黑社會會出黎，係因為佢地好易俾人煽動/收錢做野。官警黑合作已經浮面，係黑社會度吹風話示威者搞佢地，佢地就衝出黎柒，當然有班人亦只係為錢。當手足打黑果陣又要防狗隻拉人，真係好高風險。<br />\n<br />\n情報的收集同發放，要有效商討行動共識呢一個前線永遠要面對的困境。當情報永遠可以即時俾敵人知道的時候，前線要傾要決定的共識就要考慮到，確唔確保到跟住你地既幾百人佢地係咪安全番到屋企。<br />\n<br />\n而點樣做到一個最好的決定，我懇求前線請先放低個人仇恨，以背後一大班手足的生命，安全，前途做最大依歸，唔好俾殺紅了眼的情緒支佩，亦唔好再用兄弟爬山做擋箭牌，你地的決定係有人會跟，係因為大家相信你地的勇氣，承擔同智慧。如果再進一步俾仇恨蒙蔽，只有更多跑得慢的手足犧牲，講完。<br />\n<br />\n希望日後再夢見大家。"},{"pid":"68ea85dbe560e62b7ba4dc61786ec3f31843f108","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"或者有人會屌我P牌仔,請隨便...."},{"pid":"bd894897ecc31457ea1bf8eee8fc470f21623a37","tid":1421020,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"082c427e538a019211860da71ff24968359a9dd5","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"邀請眾冷氣軍師討論計策，保障手足安全"},{"pid":"8275d1a0ad29df549f523976598a1aba7d5351c4","tid":1421020,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffb71b41e962e691b2d79bafa0935f9fce1141d","tid":1421020,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0e0259c2a45e7366ba30772a61e1f2595313f8","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"再黎想講講TG GP問題，一樣，狗同黑社會要入GP係極之容易，去到現埸/集會問手足就可以入，TG GP入面閒閒地幾百到上萬人，有好多情緒的說話，無人知道真身係咩人，去到呢刻，我真係信政權可以請黑社會係入面放流料同帶風，一分散又黎警黑合作收割人頭，所有野都只可以靠係現埸的討論同共識去保護自己，保護大家，點樣係現埸有效討論同決策始終係關鍵，網上既野可能真係交俾和理非重點處理，包括TG GP"},{"pid":"1b919ca69657fa579bb584c2b4f6cdf46b87c022","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"唔記得有一點, 係有人影到警察係警署/警車入面換晒黑裝.....證據確鑿, 需要應對無間道"},{"pid":"e34fef6e8fd9793fcdbb34b1fdc828a4ea713761","tid":1421020,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d146a77a8542d470664c99aaf1bf071407802f8d","tid":1421020,"uid":122031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"Take care bro"},{"pid":"bde0d6df2dc2c587a1058086dad47e586a6ce517","tid":1421020,"uid":248290,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518d0683f703b456a85fb571ff38a60d9fc71a6b","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde0d6df2dc2c587a1058086dad47e586a6ce517","tid":1421020,"uid":248290,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c631ac1d0f42d137e5a6163f3b0b3ffc2beb80f9","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"尋日浸大學生會會長一事，休班警有4人都係黑衫黑褲,一齊係鴨寮街出現。休班時間咁岩4個黑衫黑褲? 又睇到警察點樣做滲入"},{"pid":"033fd17c3b09f4e77f1dcb38274e4478261879ad","tid":1421020,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"又屈前線 殺紅了眼"},{"pid":"4bf013c3eab7ec9ef24940648b7961536087c9b5","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033fd17c3b09f4e77f1dcb38274e4478261879ad","tid":1421020,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"又屈前線 殺紅了眼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"無意屈前線，但而家的局面所謂前線定無間道已經難分，而本文想提醒前線手足在現埸的決策需要考慮呢點"},{"pid":"60aab48305690bfdbfbc0043ff9619d7d2605e63","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"各位前線手足請注意，黑警係警署換黑衫、警黑合作、4個黑衫黑褲休班警拉浸大學生會會長、尋晚深水埗街坊疑似俾便衣狗阻礙被捕等等、敵人早已深入敵陣，係前線假扮手足收集第1手資訊作行動部處。<br />\n<br />\n前線手足請思考如何在前線現埸確保手足安全，係現埸我地無辦法阻止對方收集情報，請前線手足思考現埸決策時對大家的安全性，同埋保護自己私隱。"},{"pid":"e9b9fb6fbca15f9c31cabd0be7f5b1cfbfd2c862","tid":1421020,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a288bbc03b84c4c9aaa6bd0248b910059fcf1e62","tid":1421020,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db86150ebeecebcac807c03781d8da4cffdc448b","tid":1421020,"uid":288154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c631ac1d0f42d137e5a6163f3b0b3ffc2beb80f9","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"尋日浸大學生會會長一事，休班警有4人都係黑衫黑褲,一齊係鴨寮街出現。休班時間咁岩4個黑衫黑褲? 又睇到警察點樣做滲入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">明顯唔可能係休班，而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狗仔隊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2e5aebfd3e91b9d808881c3fe37aaf64dd7280f4","tid":1421020,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c631ac1d0f42d137e5a6163f3b0b3ffc2beb80f9","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"尋日浸大學生會會長一事，休班警有4人都係黑衫黑褲,一齊係鴨寮街出現。休班時間咁岩4個黑衫黑褲? 又睇到警察點樣做滲入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">警方一早收到線報，有線報就係有鬼啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bddac32ac3f8406c80cfc346b7b52c28e7668f94","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e5aebfd3e91b9d808881c3fe37aaf64dd7280f4","tid":1421020,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c631ac1d0f42d137e5a6163f3b0b3ffc2beb80f9","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"尋日浸大學生會會長一事，休班警有4人都係黑衫黑褲,一齊係鴨寮街出現。休班時間咁岩4個黑衫黑褲? 又睇到警察點樣做滲入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">警方一早收到線報，有線報就係有鬼啦</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"下流手段，防不勝防"},{"pid":"d700ba0d351d283e5e358dabea0933831db6719d","tid":1421020,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e27cb4aa1bbfea86a3a90d7360057d52d8268226","tid":1421020,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"